text: "Fine and Mellow" is a jazz standard written by Billie Holiday. Fine and Mellow may also refer to: * Fine and Mellow (Ella Fitzgerald album), 1979 * Fine and Mellow (Etta Jones album), 1986 * Fine and Mellow: Live at Birdland West, a 1988 album by Carmen McRae
title: Fine and Mellow (disambiguation)
